nodes.text: Zunor was a female Cathar who served as a Jedi Master of the Jedi Order before she joined the radicalized Order of Revan during the Galactic War. Zunor was among the Revanite commanders who led the Revanite forces in defense of the Temple of Sacrifice during the battle on Yavin 4. Zunor was slain in the Massassi village by forces from the Imperial-Republic Yavin Coalition.

Master Zunor appears in Star Wars: The Old Republic: Shadow of Revan, a 2014 Digital Expansion for the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic, and is one of four named enemies that must be defeated by players in the mission "The Enemy Within."
